text.data-name: Before you think about whether clothes are right for you, consider whether you are the right person for them.
Live a life that suits you best. That is the ultimate luxury.
text.tspan: Live a life that suits you best.

text.data-name: Life is not a beauty contest. There are good people who are not beautiful. I just dont like people with bad temper.
I dont like ordinary beauty. There is no beauty without weirdness.
